tructure to improve generalization in ultra-sparse regimes (<50 labels/annotator), where traditional consensus signals fail. By treating annotator reliability as a relational, emergent property rather than an isolated metric, RCR enhances model robustness, reduces calibration error, and provides interpretable trust graphs. Potential impact includes safer deployment in clinical AI, citizen science, and other domains reliant on heterogeneous human judgments.",
